snippet.title: 12 Labours of Hercules VIII: How I Met Megara
snippet.description:
Hercules meets a sobbing young lady on the shore. She tells him a story of her younger sister, who just has been kidnapped by the evil Cretans, as well as her cat. Bragging warriors leave a clue. Now, Hercules has to travel in attempt to find the girl, and maybe have a 
chance to get on Megara’s good side.

- More depth with sub-levels
- Romance & cute kittens
- See how Hercules looked before becoming a Hero
- Easy to learn, hard to master: many ways to complete a level
- Mummies & Pyramid
